Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: gale
Version: 0.0.2
Summary: Sugar for Tornado Asynchrous HTTP client
Home-page: https://github.com/simpx/gale
Author: simpx
Author-email: simpxx@gmail.com
License: BSD
Description: Gale
        =========
        Gale is just Tornado
        
        Installation
        ---------
            $ pip install gale
        
        Asynchrous HTTP Request
        ----------
        
        ###Get
            import gale
            def handle(response):
                print response.body
                gale.stop()
                
            gale.get('http://httpbin.org/ip', callback=handle)
            gale.start()
        ###Post
            gale.post('http://httpbin.org/post', data={'a':1}, callback=handle)
            gale.start()
        ###Proxy and Cookies
            gale.get('http://httpbin.org/get',
                     params={'a':1, 'b':2},
                     proxy='user:pass@8.8.8.8:80',
                     cookies={'token': 'asdfgh'}, callback=handle)
            gale.start()
        
        Task
        ----------
            def all_done():
                print 'all requests complete!'
                gale.stop()
                
            task = gale.Task()
            task.add(gale.get, 'http://httpbin.org/ip', callback=handle)
            task.add(gale.get, 'http://httpbin.org/get', callback=handle)
            task.add(gale.post, 'http://httpbin.org/post', data={'a': 1},
                     callback=handle)
                     
            task.run(all_done)
